# Extension body

```scalascript
case class Holder[A](value: Any)
case class PRegex(pattern: String)

extension [A](h: Holder[(A, A)])
  def current: Any = h.value
  def plus(n: Int): Int = h.value + n
```

# Dedented top-level code unit

```scalascript
def classify(p: Any, fallback: String): String =
  p match
    case PRegex(pattern) => pattern
    case _               => fallback
```
